test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)

 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7572a16665c0> = [[1, -33], [1, -33, 1], [-33, 1], [-33, 1, -33], [1, -33], [1, -33, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -1089 == -33
 +  where -1089 = <built-in function prod>([-3, -11, -33])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
